{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/computer-network/네트워크-레이어-(2)/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"10cheon00의 Archive"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"535f40a9-d853-5f06-adb6-8390aec9ac94","excerpt":"컴퓨터 네트워크 수업을 듣고 정리한 내용입니다. 컨트롤 영역 네트워크는 데이터 영역과 컨트롤 영역으로 나뉨. 컨트롤 영역의 구조는 두 가지가 있음 per-router control(traditional) 각 라우터가 알고리즘을 통해 스스로 포워딩 테이블을 구성 Software…","html":"<p>컴퓨터 네트워크 수업을 듣고 정리한 내용입니다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"컨트롤-영역\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%BB%A8%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%A4-%EC%98%81%EC%97%AD\" aria-label=\"컨트롤 영역 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>컨트롤 영역</h1>\n<p>네트워크는 데이터 영역과 컨트롤 영역으로 나뉨.</p>\n<p>컨트롤 영역의 구조는 두 가지가 있음</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>per-router control(traditional)</p>\n<p>각 라우터가 알고리즘을 통해 스스로 포워딩 테이블을 구성</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Software Define Networking</p>\n<p>원격 컨트롤러가 계산한 포워딩 테이블을 모든 라우터에게 설정</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"라우팅-프로토콜의-목표\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%9D%BC%EC%9A%B0%ED%8C%85-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%86%A0%EC%BD%9C%EC%9D%98-%EB%AA%A9%ED%91%9C\" aria-label=\"라우팅 프로토콜의 목표 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>라우팅 프로토콜의 목표</h1>\n<p>네트워크 속 라우터를 통해 시작 지점부터 도착 지점 사이의 최적의 경로(최소 비용, 최대 속도, 최소 혼잡도 등)를 설정하는 것</p>\n<h1 id=\"link-state-dijkstra-알고리즘\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#link-state-dijkstra-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\" aria-label=\"link state dijkstra 알고리즘 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Link-state: Dijkstra 알고리즘</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>모든 노드(라우터)가 같은 정보를 공유한다.</li>\n<li>Link state의 브로드캐스트를 통해 전달된다.</li>\n<li>각 노드마다 모든 노드로 향하는 최소 비용의 경로를 계산한다.</li>\n<li>최소 비용을 계산하는 데에 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n^2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span> 의 시간복잡도를 갖는다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"oscillation-possible\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#oscillation-possible\" aria-label=\"oscillation possible permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Oscillation possible</h2>\n<p>노드(라우터)간 비용이 달라졌을 때 경로가 계속 변경되어 진동하는 것처럼 보이는 것.</p>\n<h1 id=\"distance-vector-bellman-ford-알고리즘\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#distance-vector-bellman-ford-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\" aria-label=\"distance vector bellman ford 알고리즘 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Distance vector: Bellman-Ford 알고리즘</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>매 시간마다 인접한 이웃 노드(라우터)에게서 전달받은 정보를 토대로 최소 비용을 계산하는 것</li>\n<li>이웃이나 자신의 link cost값이 변경되었을 때 계산을 바로 할 수 있음.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"good-news-travels-fast-bad-news-travels-slow\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#good-news-travels-fast-bad-news-travels-slow\" aria-label=\"good news travels fast bad news travels slow permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>good news travels fast, bad news travels slow</h2>\n<p>link cost값이 더 작은 값으로 바뀌면 금방 갱신되지만 link cost값이 더 큰 값으로 바뀌면 느리게 갱신되는 것.</p>\n<p>최악의 경우 무한번 반복할 수도 있다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"autonomous-systems\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#autonomous-systems\" aria-label=\"autonomous systems permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Autonomous systems</h1>\n<p>이상적인 모델을 현실적으로 적용하기 위해 만든 작은 네트워크 집합.</p>\n<p>한 지역에 있는 라우터들의 집합을 말한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"intra-as\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intra-as\" aria-label=\"intra as permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Intra-AS</h2>\n<p>내부 도메인 라우팅을 말한다.</p>\n<p>같은 AS에 있는 라우터들은 동일한 프로토콜을 사용하여 포워딩 테이블을 구성한다.</p>\n<p>다른 AS에 있는 라우터와 연결된 라우터들을 gateway router라고 명칭한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"inter-as\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inter-as\" aria-label=\"inter as permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Inter-AS</h2>\n<p>AS간 또는 도메인간 라우팅을 말한다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>intra as내의 라우터들은 같은 as내에 있는 라우터들로 향하는 포워딩 테이블을 갖지만 gateway router들은 intra-as 포워딩 테이블과 inter-as 포워딩 테이블을 갖는다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"intra-as-routing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intra-as-routing\" aria-label=\"intra as routing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Intra-AS routing</h1>\n<p>외부로 나가기 위해 어떤 게이트웨이 라우터를 선택할지 결정하는 프로토콜 사용. RIP, EIGRP, OSPF가 있음</p>\n<h2 id=\"ospf\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ospf\" aria-label=\"ospf permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>OSPF</h2>\n<p>Link-state방식 사용. IP를 사용하여 정보를 주고 받는다.</p>\n<p>각 라우터가 OSPF 프로토콜로 정보를 주고받아 같은 AS에 있는 모든 라우터와 정보를 공유한다. 공유한 정보를 토대로 각 라우터는 포워딩 테이블을 구성한다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"hierarchical-ospf\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hierarchical-ospf\" aria-label=\"hierarchical ospf permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Hierarchical OSPF</h3>\n<p>Dijkstra 알고리즘을 사용하려면 <span class=\"math math-inline\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>O</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><msup><mi>n</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">O(n^2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.064108em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">O</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">n</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8141079999999999em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">2</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span></span> 의 비용을 써야 한다. AS가 너무 크면 계산하기 힘들기 때문에 AS의 계층을 상위와 하위로 나눈다.</p>\n<p>Link-state 정보는 각 area 또는 backbone 내에서만 전파된다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Local area</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Local routers</p>\n<p>area 내의 라우터들에 대한 포워딩 테이블을 갖는다.</p>\n<p>area 밖으로 나가는 패킷은 area border router에게 포워딩한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Area border router</p>\n<p>라우터가 속한 area로 향하는 비용을 요약해서 backbone에 전파한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Backbone</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Backbone router</p>\n<p>서로 다른 area를 연결하는 라우터</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Boundary router</p>\n<p>다른 AS와 연결되는 라우터.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"inter-as-routing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#inter-as-routing\" aria-label=\"inter as routing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Inter-AS routing</h1>\n<p>BGP(border gateway protocol)을 사용한다.</p>\n<p>서브넷이 자신의 존재를 알려서 다른 인터넷에서 접속이 가능하도록 만든다.</p>\n<p>BGP는 eBGP와 iBGP로 나뉜다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>eBGP(외부 BGP)</p>\n<p>다른 서브넷의 정보를 획득하는 것.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>iBGP(내부 BGP)</p>\n<p>자신의 서브넷에 대한 정보를 모든 내부 도메인 즉, Intra AS내의 라우터에 뿌리는 것.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/88237c015c5ed34bdd7681a28cbf1fdc/c67d4/image-1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.645569620253163%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Alt text\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/88237c015c5ed34bdd7681a28cbf1fdc/f058b/image-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/88237c015c5ed34bdd7681a28cbf1fdc/c26ae/image-1.png 158w,\n/static/88237c015c5ed34bdd7681a28cbf1fdc/6bdcf/image-1.png 315w,\n/static/88237c015c5ed34bdd7681a28cbf1fdc/f058b/image-1.png 630w,\n/static/88237c015c5ed34bdd7681a28cbf1fdc/c67d4/image-1.png 723w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>두 BGP 라우터가 세션을 구성하여 반영구적으로 계속 BGP 메세지를 주고 받는다. 새로운 라우터(위 사진의 라우터 X)가 서브넷에 가입되면 eBGP를 통해 다른 AS에 전파되고, 그 AS에서는 iBGP를 통해 AS 내부의 라우터에 전파된다.</p>\n<p>BGP는 prefix와 attributes를 전파한다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>prefix</p>\n<p>전파될 도착 지점</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>attributes</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>AS-PATH</p>\n<p>prefix가 전파되면서 거쳐간 AS들의 목록</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>NEXT-HOP</p>\n<p>다음으로 전파될 내부의 AS 라우터를 의미한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>BGP는 정책에 기반한 라우팅을 한다.</p>\n<p>예시로, 게이트웨이 라우터는 같은 도착 지점에 대해서 다수의 경로 정보를 전달받을 수 있는데, 이 때 정책에 의해 경로가 더 짧은 것을 선택할 수 있다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"bgp-messages\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#bgp-messages\" aria-label=\"bgp messages permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>BGP Messages</h2>\n<p>BGP는 TCP를 사용하여 정보를 주고 받는다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>OPEN</p>\n<p>두 BGP 라우터(peer) 간 TCP 세션을 구성한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>UPDATE</p>\n<p>새로운 경로를 전달하거나, 기존의 경로를 삭제한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>KEEPALIVE</p>\n<p>경로의 업데이트가 없을 때에도 연결을 유지한다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>NOTIFICATION</p>\n<p>이전 메세지의 오류를 수정한다. 또는 연결을 종료한다.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote>\n<p>iBGP를 통해 다른 AS로 향하기 위해 어떤 게이트웨이 라우터를 선택해야하는지 알게 되면 OSPF로 AS 내부의 모든 라우터에게 그 정보가 전파되어 포워딩 테이블을 구성하게 된다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"hot-potato-routing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#hot-potato-routing\" aria-label=\"hot potato routing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Hot potato routing</h2>\n<p>inter-AS에서 계산된 비용은 생각하지 않고 intra-AS내에서 게이트웨이까지 나가는 비용이 가장 작은 경로를 선택하게 되는 것.</p>\n<h2 id=\"intra-as와-inter-as의-차이점\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#intra-as%EC%99%80-inter-as%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\" aria-label=\"intra as와 inter as의 차이점 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Intra-AS와 Inter-AS의 차이점</h2>\n<h3 id=\"정책\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EC%B1%85\" aria-label=\"정책 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>정책</h3>\n<p>intra-AS에서는 정책으로 관리하지 않기에 중요하지 않지만, inter-AS에서는 관리자가 트래픽 관리를 위해 정책을 설정하게 된다.</p>\n<h3 id=\"성능\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%84%B1%EB%8A%A5\" aria-label=\"성능 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>성능</h3>\n<p>계층을 나눔으로써 intra-AS는 오직 성능에만 집중할 수 있지만 inter-AS는 정책이 우선된다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"software-define-networking\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#software-define-networking\" aria-label=\"software define networking permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Software Define Networking</h1>\n<p>각 라우터가 link-state 정보를 확인하고 경로를 업데이트 하는 방법은 실시간으로 적용하기 어렵다. 그래서 원격 컨트롤러에게 맡긴다.</p>\n<p>SDN은 3개의 계층로 분리된다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"data-plane-switch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#data-plane-switch\" aria-label=\"data plane switch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Data-plane Switch</h2>\n<p>단순하게 포워딩 테이블에 의한 패킷 스위칭을 담당한다. (generalized data-plane forwarding 사용)</p>\n<p>상위 계층인 컨트롤러에게 API를 제공하여 포워딩 테이블을 관리할 수 있다.</p>\n<p>OpenFlow 프로토콜를 사용하여 컨트롤러와 통신한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sdn-controllernetwork-os\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#sdn-controllernetwork-os\" aria-label=\"sdn controllernetwork os permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>SDN Controller(network OS)</h2>\n<p>네트워크의 정보를 수집, 관리한다.</p>\n<p>상위 계층인 애플리케이션에게 API를 제공하여 알고리즘을 구현할 때 포워딩 테이블을 수정할 수 있도록 한다.</p>\n<p>스위치가 제공하는 API를 통해 상호작용한다.</p>\n<p>트래픽 관리 시스템을 구현한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"application\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#application\" aria-label=\"application permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Application</h2>\n<p>컨트롤러가 제공하는 API를 통해 라우팅, 로드밸런싱 같은 알고리즘을 구현한다.</p>\n<p>컨트롤러와는 독립적으로, 서드파티에 의해 구현될 수도 있다.(?)</p>\n<h1 id=\"openflow-protocol\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#openflow-protocol\" aria-label=\"openflow protocol permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>OpenFlow Protocol</h1>\n<p>컨트롤러와 스위치 사이에서 메세지를 주고받는 규칙이다. TCP를 사용한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"controller-to-switch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#controller-to-switch\" aria-label=\"controller to switch permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Controller to Switch</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>feature : 스위치의 정보를 쿼리로 긁어온다.</li>\n<li>configure : 스위치의 파라미터를 수정한다.</li>\n<li>modify-state : OpenFlow Table에 엔트리를 추가/삭제/수정한다.</li>\n<li>packet-out : 컨트롤러가 직접 특정 스위치의 포트로 패킷을 내보낸다...(?)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"switch-to-controller\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#switch-to-controller\" aria-label=\"switch to controller permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Switch to Controller</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>packet-in : 패킷을 컨트롤러에게 보낸다.</li>\n<li>flow-removed : OpenFlow Table에서 특정 엔트리가 지워졌음을 알린다.</li>\n<li>port status : 포트의 상태를 알림. 포트가 변경되었을 때 알리는 것 같다.</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"상호작용-흐름\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%81%ED%98%B8%EC%9E%91%EC%9A%A9-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\" aria-label=\"상호작용 흐름 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>상호작용 흐름</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>어떤 오류가 발생하여 <code class=\"language-text\">port status</code>를 통해 컨트롤러에게 알린다.</li>\n<li>컨트롤러는 메세지를 수신하여 DB에 저장된 link state의 정보를 수정하고, 애플리케이션에 알린다.</li>\n<li>애플리케이션은 상태가 변경되었을 때 Dijkstra 알고리즘을 다시 수행하도록 설정하고 있다. 그러므로 다시 실행되어 경로를 업데이트한다.</li>\n<li>애플리케이션이 알고리즘을 실행하면, 컨트롤러에 저장된 정보를 조회하기 위해 상호작용한다.</li>\n<li>업데이트된 경로를 전파하기 위해 애플리케이션이 컨트롤러를 통해 각 스위치의 FlowTable을 업데이트한다.</li>\n</ol>\n<blockquote>\n<p>여기까지 중간고사 범위</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"icmp\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#icmp\" aria-label=\"icmp permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>ICMP</h1>\n<p>호스트와 라우터 사이에 데이터 전송과 관련된 문제를 알리기 위한 프로토콜. IP를 사용하지만 payload에 담겨서 전송된다.</p>\n<p>TTL이 0이면 전송된 패킷을 버리고 src로 ICMP 오류코드(type: 11, code: 0)가 담긴 메세지를 보낸다.</p>\n<h1 id=\"network-management\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#network-management\" aria-label=\"network management permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>Network Management</h1>\n<p>네트워크에 존재하는 관리시스템이 각 디바이스에 연결된 에이전트를 통해 관리한다.</p>\n<p>각 디바이스의 MIB정보를 조회, 수정하기 위해서 SNMP 프로토콜을 사용한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"snmp-프로토콜-메세지\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#snmp-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%86%A0%EC%BD%9C-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%B8%EC%A7%80\" aria-label=\"snmp 프로토콜 메세지 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>SNMP 프로토콜 메세지</h2>\n<h3 id=\"시스템\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%9C\" aria-label=\"시스템 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>시스템</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>정보 검색 : GetRequest, GetNextRequest, GetBulkRequest</li>\n<li>정보 업데이트 : SetRequest</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"에이전트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%97%90%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%84%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"에이전트 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>에이전트</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>시스템의 요청에 대한 응답 : Response</li>\n<li>자발적으로 알림 : Trap (이슈가 생겼을 때 시스템에게 알림)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Get~, Set~은 format이 동일하지만 Trap 메세지만 다른 format이다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"mibmanagement-information-base\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#mibmanagement-information-base\" aria-label=\"mibmanagement information base permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z\"></path></svg></a>MIB(Management Information Base)</h2>\n<p>망 관리를 위해 사용되는 관리 정보</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"네트워크 레이어 (2)","date":"October 20, 2023","description":null,"tags":["computer-network"]},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%BB%A8%ED%8A%B8%EB%A1%A4-%EC%98%81%EC%97%AD\">컨트롤 영역</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EB%9D%BC%EC%9A%B0%ED%8C%85-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%86%A0%EC%BD%9C%EC%9D%98-%EB%AA%A9%ED%91%9C\">라우팅 프로토콜의 목표</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#link-state-dijkstra-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\">Link-state: Dijkstra 알고리즘</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#oscillation-possible\">Oscillation possible</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#distance-vector-bellman-ford-%EC%95%8C%EA%B3%A0%EB%A6%AC%EC%A6%98\">Distance vector: Bellman-Ford 알고리즘</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#good-news-travels-fast-bad-news-travels-slow\">good news travels fast, bad news travels slow</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#autonomous-systems\">Autonomous systems</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#intra-as\">Intra-AS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#inter-as\">Inter-AS</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#intra-as-routing\">Intra-AS routing</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#ospf\">OSPF</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#hierarchical-ospf\">Hierarchical OSPF</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#inter-as-routing\">Inter-AS routing</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#bgp-messages\">BGP Messages</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#hot-potato-routing\">Hot potato routing</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#intra-as%EC%99%80-inter-as%EC%9D%98-%EC%B0%A8%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%90\">Intra-AS와 Inter-AS의 차이점</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A0%95%EC%B1%85\">정책</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%84%B1%EB%8A%A5\">성능</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#software-define-networking\">Software Define Networking</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#data-plane-switch\">Data-plane Switch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#sdn-controllernetwork-os\">SDN Controller(network OS)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#application\">Application</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#openflow-protocol\">OpenFlow Protocol</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#controller-to-switch\">Controller to Switch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#switch-to-controller\">Switch to Controller</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%EC%83%81%ED%98%B8%EC%9E%91%EC%9A%A9-%ED%9D%90%EB%A6%84\">상호작용 흐름</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#icmp\">ICMP</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#network-management\">Network Management</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#snmp-%ED%94%84%EB%A1%9C%ED%86%A0%EC%BD%9C-%EB%A9%94%EC%84%B8%EC%A7%80\">SNMP 프로토콜 메세지</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%8B%9C%EC%8A%A4%ED%85%9C\">시스템</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%97%90%EC%9D%B4%EC%A0%84%ED%8A%B8\">에이전트</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#mibmanagement-information-base\">MIB(Management Information Base)</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>"},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/computer-network/네트워크-레이어-(1)/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"네트워크 레이어 (1)"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/computer-organization/컴퓨터-구조론-(1)-컴퓨터-추상화-및-관련-기술/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"컴퓨터 구조론 (1) - 컴퓨터 추상화 및 관련 기술"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"535f40a9-d853-5f06-adb6-8390aec9ac94","previousPostId":"e3648d63-0812-58de-917b-2b45f4fad1a1","nextPostId":"4dd86b97-401e-5412-afc0-af3fe6a82db4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["230163734","3589320610"],"slicesMap":{}}